            <div class="field field--name-name field--type-string field--label-hidden field__item">13.1</div>
      </h4>
        <p class="goal-text">Strengthen resilience and adaptive capacity to climate-related hazards and natural disasters in all countries</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="indicators">
    <div class="indicators-header">
